OL,7,FTributes have been paid to a father
OL,8,Fwho died in a crash shortly after
OL,9,Ftaking part in a motorcycle convoy for
OL,10,Fa boy's funeral.
OL,12,FChris Bailey died in an incident near
OL,13,Fhis home in Hay-on-Wye. He was one of
OL,14,Fa number of bikers who paid tribute to
OL,15,F14-year-old Kyle Sieniawski.
OL,17,FKyle was one of the youngest people in
OL,18,Fthe UK ever to be diagnosed with motor
OL,19,Fneurone disease.
