OL,7,FA fundraiser set up in Mr Bailey's
OL,8,Fmemory said: "If you're here, you'll
OL,9,Fknow that Chris sadly passed away on
OL,10,FFriday, 19th December whilst riding
OL,11,Fhome from a funeral ride to support
OL,12,Fsuperhero Kyle. Chris was a loved and
OL,13,Fmuch-respected member of the Valley
OL,14,FCommandos MC Powys chapter."
OL,16,FKyle's family also shared a tribute to
OL,17,FMr Bailey on Kyle's MND Story Facebook
OL,18,Fpage. They said: "We're absolutely
OL,19,Fdevastated to hear that one of the
OL,20,Fbikers tragically lost his life whilst
OL,21,Ftravelling home from Kyle's funeral.
