OL,7,F"Chris Bailey was a valued member of
OL,8,Fthe Powys Chapter Valley Commandos and
OL,9,Fto lose his life after doing such an
OL,10,Famazing gesture is just cruel beyond
OL,11,Fwords.
OL,13,F"Our hearts are breaking for his
OL,14,Ffamily, and Christmas is just days
OL,15,Faway. Life can be so cruel. We're
OL,16,Fthinking of all his family, friends,
OL,17,Fand also his comrades at the Valley
OL,18,FCommandos. Heaven has gained another
OL,19,Fangel way too soon."
